ves provides aboveaverage returns over the longterm fairfax was founded in  by the present chairman and chief executive officer v prem watsa the company has been under present management since  and is headquartered in toronto canada its common shares are listed on the toronto stock exchange under the symbol ffh and in us dollars under the symbol ffhu fairfax’s insurance and reinsurance companies operate on a decentralized basis with autonomous management teams applying a focused underwriting strategy to their markets fairfax subsidiaries provide a full range of property and casualty products maintaining a diversified portfolio of risks across all classes of business geographic regions and types of insureds since  investments have been centrally managed for all of the fairfax group companies by hamblin watsa investment counsel ltd wwwhwicca a whollyowned subsidiary of fairfax hamblin watsa emphasizes a conservative value investment philosophy seeking to invest assets on a total return basis which includes realized and unrealized gains over the longterm   fairfax financial holdings limited global links legal notice site map login powered by q inc  hamblin watsa investment counsel company profile  owler we just sent you an email to verify your account check your inbox     resend verification link  sign in sign in sign up you have just joined  job information managing director date posted jun   job type full time career level executive industry business and professional services job function accounting and finance managing director hamblin watsa investment counsel ltd toronto on canada apply now you need to sign in to apply to this job register sign in hamblin watsa investment counsel ltd  contact us about hamblin watsainvestment performancecorporate accessibility policy contact us contact us mailing address  wellington street west suite  toronto ontario canada mj n contact paul rivett chief operating officer   privetthwicca   hamblin watsa investment counsel ltd powere